snippet.title: Soulframe | Official Cinematic Reveal
snippet.description:
Declare your Envoy at https://www.soulframe.com! 
Join us at https://www.instagram.com/playsoulframe.

Digital Extremes proudly revealed an all-new IP, Soulframe, during #TennoCon 2022. This free-to-play open world adventure is heavily influenced by themes of nature, restoration, and exploration. 

A totally new game in early development, #Soulframe will deliver its own independent and uniquely immersive experience led by the creative and imaginative minds behind Warframe. For early fans of Digital Extremes, the path to release will be a familiar one: it will be a transparent, collaborative and iterative process that is shaped by the passion of players and DE. Anyone who wants to join us on our development journey and see more about the game can visit the official website now: https://www.soulframe.com
